### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → DOCTORS — /api/v1/admin/doctors
### ============================================================================

### List doctor applications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/doctors/applications
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Approve doctor application
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/doctors/applications/{{doctorUserId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Reject doctor application
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/doctors/applications/{{doctorUserId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Insufficient credentials"
}

### Invite doctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/doctors/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "doctor@example.com",
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doctor"
}

### Get doctor stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/doctors/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### List doctors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Revoke doctor privileges
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/doctors/{{doctorUserId}}/revoke
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
